Package: opencpn
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libgps19
Recommends: gpsd, opencpn-data, opencpn-doc, xtide-coastline
Suggests: gpsd-clients, xcalib
Description: GPS ChartPlotter/Navigator
 OpenCPN is a concise ship-borne GUI chart plotter
 application supporting:
 .
     * GPS/GPDS Postition Input
     * BSB Raster Chart Display
     * S57 Vector ENChart Display
     * AIS Input Decoding
     * Waypoint Autopilot Navigation

Package: opencpn-doc
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Section: doc
Suggests: opencpn
Description: Documentation for OpenCPN, a GPS ChartPlotter/Navigator
 OpenCPN is a concise ship-borne GUI chart plotter application.
 .   
 This package contains the HTML documentation for OpenCPN.

Package: opencpn-data
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: opencpn
Description: Tidal harmonics and audio files for OpenCPN
 OpenCPN is a concise ship-borne GUI chart plotter application.
 .
 This package contains the tidal harmonics and audio files for OpenCPN.
